text: Atimiola rickstanleyi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lingafelter and Nearns in 2007. It is known from the Dominican Republic.BioLib.cz - Atimiola rickstanleyi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2007
